it is a mediator, which get invoked before or after your actual code.

mycustominterceptor implements HandleInterceptor
and implement this methods
prehandle
posthandle
aftercompletion

in app config you have to register your interceptor to spring.

it is like all middleware actions for an incoming http request

flow :
req came
prehandle of your interceptor
controller main logic
post handle
after completion

using custom annotation

for custom annotation interceptor

invoke it in interceptor class using @annotation in @Around

catch result in it then send that to client. means aspect returns the value catched from your controller

